{"tid":1369530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警反對 7.28 上環遊行","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:30:17.000Z","uid":271002,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5ec49864dcb74ba6c1f47402137c9f56a3774a","tid":1369530,"uid":271002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"<strong>警反對 7.28 上環遊行 僅容許遮打花園集會</strong><br />\n<br />\n7月28日上環遊行發起人劉頴匡向傳媒表示，在周五晚上近凌晨時分接獲警方通知，反對舉行遊行及禁止在終點中山紀念公園的集會，只允許在起點遮打花園進行公眾集會。<br />\n<br />\n劉頴匡表示，將會向遊行集會上訴委員會提出上訴，並要求在星期六聆訊。按照警方的反對通知書條文，警方反對遊行及終點集會的理由只有一個，就是以往類似議題的遊行集會，在結束後都發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，警方這個理由，等同封殺以後所有與反送中有關的公眾活動，是明目張膽地打壓異見，剝奪《基本法》賦予香港不同政見市民平等享受的集會自由。7.28 遊行主辦方呼籲所有捍衛港人基本權利的市民，出席獲警方允許舉行的合法活動，在下午三時到遮打花園集會，「港人必須企出來，用雙腳捍衛自己的遊行集會權利。」<br />\n<br />\n發言人劉頴匡表示，會在上訴聆訊後決定如何處理遊行活動安排，希望上訴委員會明白今次警方反對的理由非同小可，嚴重侵蝕港人的憲制權利，必須推翻警方的決定，捍衛《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-7-28-%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E5%83%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%B1%E9%81%AE%E6%89%93%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-7-28-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2592%25B0%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E5%2583%2585%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E9%2581%25AE%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwU5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=f564f6af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-7-28-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2592%25B0%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E5%2583%2585%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E9%2581%25AE%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=c61bac38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-7-28-%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E5%83%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%A8%B1%E9%81%AE%E6%89%93%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83/</a>"},{"pid":"9cc385ea5c7221894eb5dec531d6bbdb2d4ce2a4","tid":1369530,"uid":64097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:16:13.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"bd829aedd1a2fa67a6fa93346a45fc5d1242cca2","tid":1369530,"uid":271002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"希望上訴推翻 ..."},{"pid":"fbc8554ed70d82d4356f3aa06283198ed8a164a8","tid":1369530,"uid":281904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:28:30.000Z","msg":"玩到咁盡，種種跡象都見到佢地就爆煲，接近政變邊緣"},{"pid":"9fbc90c611900c8800a57c616aadbe6ac920bf00","tid":1369530,"uid":235458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:34:59.000Z","msg":"其實如果佢個理由係以往公眾活動後都會爆發衝突 咁點解佢又會批遮打花園集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f875d705d506044792421d941ec1703721ec9ff8","tid":1369530,"uid":271002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:37:01.000Z","msg":"Stiring up troubles and testing boundaries ... <br />\nHope 727 successful, show 警方反對 useless."},{"pid":"f918bd748b427a38f67040dae991946282a1850e","tid":1369530,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:51:36.000Z","msg":"又反對！這只會讓民意更沸騰！"},{"pid":"a7f398b15699f03a14e8ee05601c4498026834d9","tid":1369530,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:25:24.000Z","msg":"以後唔駛遊行lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二哥軍政府統治香港，連一哥政務司司長都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de18cfc59dd211856adb56cad7aaeb363372615d","tid":1369530,"uid":263883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:30:17.000Z","msg":"理得佢反唔反對都會照出 你愈唔俾我出我就愈想出<img src=\"/assets/f